title: Fire Watch Face
summary: Maltese cross analog watch face contains Star of Life, fire hydrant and others.
description: Fire watch face is a fire and Rescue maltese cross. It contains a Star of life as well as a hydrant and other fire related symbols. This watch face has been tested on an LG G Watch and a Moto 360 Sport.

recentChanges: Added ticks around the outside of the image.
Added background behind hot word and other icons to make them easier to see.
Now tested on a Moto 360 sport.
